<p style="margin:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（一）被保险人享受安阳市医保待遇，但未经过安阳市基本医保结算的，本产品不承担相应的保险责任。</span></span></span></span></p>

