<p style="margin:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><b><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">十三、解除合同</span></span></b></span></span></p>

