<p style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0cm 40px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:10.5pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">4.</span></span><span style="font-size:11.0pt"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">本人/本人监护人确认符合参保条件。</span></span></span></span></p>

